r value (H_0 = 72 +/- 8 km s-1 Mpc-1). A more realistic singular\nisothermal sphere model plus external shear gives H_0 = 51.7 +4.0 -3.0 km s-1\nMpc-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jun 2006 16:08:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2007 15:12:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
