ction\nplanning. The implementation of the process rules into a clinical setting is\neasy since only a sagittal radiography is required. The osteotomy size can be\nmonitored using optical guided instruments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Jun 2006 14:15:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
